---
import Angular from "../components/icons/Angular.astro"



---

<section class="bg-[#f9f9f9] py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <!-- Título -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">
        <span class="bg-yellow-300 px-2 border-2 border-black">Proyectos</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
        Desarrollé soluciones reales durante mis prácticas preprofesionales, mejorando procesos en negocios locales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de proyectos -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Proyecto 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-black p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Chelas Grill</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
          Jokester began sneaking into the castle in the middle of the night and leaving jokes all over the place: under the king’s pillow, in his soup, even in the royal toilet. The king was furious, but he couldn’t seem to stop Jokester. And then, one day, the people of the kingdom discovered that the jokes left by Jokester were so funny that they couldn’t help but laugh. And once they started laughing, they couldn’t stop.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex space-x-4">
          <Angular class="w-8 h-8" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen o demo -->
      <div class="bg-gray-200 border-2 border-black flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="text-lg font-medium">Imagen o demo</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Proyecto 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-black p-6 shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Chelas Grill</h3>
